00:10:00.142 --> 00:10:02.881
tot op zo'n 15 meter nauwkeurig.

00:10:03.261 --> 00:10:06.355
Onze cybercriminelen hadden hetzelfde gedaan.

00:10:06.355 --> 00:10:09.473
